casebody.head_matter:
Roy Allen GREEN, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES.
No. 18-8435.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 15, 2019.
Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.
Justice SOTOMAYOR, which whom Justice GINSBURG joins, dissenting from the denial of certiorari: I dissent for the reasons set out in Brown v. United States, 586 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 14, 202 L.Ed.2d 302 (2018) ( Sotomayor, J., dissenting).
